06 or similar), use interface for now\n658: - **Testing Strategy**: Follow TDD manifest from `testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md`\n659: - **Stage ST-3**: Design complete, ready for implementation breakdown\n660: - **Reference**: `sandbox-orchestration/AR-005-sandbox-creation-processor/design.md` contains full specification\n661: - **Code Style**: Follow existing patterns in pkg/workloadmanager (chi router, Handler interface)\n662: - **TDD**: Write tests before implementation for each component\n663: - **Rollback**: Critical requirement - ensure all failure paths clean up resources\n664: - **Timeout**: 2-minute sandbox creation timeout is hard requirement from spec\n665: - **WarmPool**: CodeInterpreter WarmPoolSize > 0 creates SandboxClaim, not full Sandbox\n\n(End of file - total 665 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Foundation - Common Types & Constants\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Create `pkg/common/types/sandbox.go` file\n  - Define `CreateSandboxRequest` struct with fields: `Kind`, `Name`, `Namespace`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-005/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775844541909,"end":1775844541939}}}}
