{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775844552059,"sessionID":"ses_2876b120affeRTtTcCrONDu2pG","part":{"id":"prt_d78956914001MF1FGS5BwVBrk0","messageID":"msg_d78954630001StyhBPfVZ2R3Qa","sessionID":"ses_2876b120affeRTtTcCrONDu2pG","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-97b655c1ffa34394966bc70faf879f95","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义 AgentRuntime CRD 的 Go 类型结构，包括:\n16: - `AgentRuntime` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n17: - `AgentRuntimeList` 类型\n18: - `CodeInterpreter` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n19: - `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n20: - 相关常量、标签、注解定义\n21: \n22: ## Out of Scope\n23: \n24: - Controller 实现\n25: - Webhook 验证逻辑\n26: - CRD YAML 生成\n27: - client-go 代码生成\n28: \n29: ## Dependencies\n30: \n31: 无外部依赖。\n32: \n33: ## Deliverables\n34: \n35: | File | Description |\n36: |------|-------------|\n37: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go` | AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter 类型定义 |\n38: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | 包文档 |\n39: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Scheme 注册 |\n40: \n41: ## Acceptance Criteria\n42: \n43: - [ ] 类型定义符合 Kubernetes API conventions\n44: - [ ] JSON tags 使用 camelCase\n45: - [ ] 包含完整的字段注释\n46: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n47: \n48: ## References\n49: \n50: - Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n\n(End of file - total 50 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 AgentRuntime CRD 的 Go 类型结构，包括:\n- `AgentRuntime` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n- `AgentRuntimeList` 类型\n- `CodeInterpreter` 类型及其 `Spec`、`Status`\n- `CodeInterpreterList` 类型\n- 相关常量、标签、注解定义","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md","time":{"start":1775844552044,"end":1775844552057}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775844552062,"sessionID":"ses_2876b120affeRTtTcCrONDu2pG","part":{"id":"prt_d78956d0f001MXOZalNtmi0Tam","messageID":"msg_d78954630001StyhBPfVZ2R3Qa","sessionID":"ses_2876b120affeRTtTcCrONDu2pG","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-aa0a2e821c3e4f15bc58d2cb6937ef13","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，包括:\n16: - HTTP 服务器配置与生命周期管理\n17: - 路由设计与中间件架构\n18: - 请求/响应数据结构定义\n19: - 健康检查与指标暴露端点\n20: - 错误处理与日志记录机制\n21: \n22: ## Out of Scope\n23: \n24: - 业务逻辑实现（Sandbox 创建、调度等）\n25: - WebSocket 连接管理\n26: - 认证授权实现\n27: - 具体业务 API 端点实现\n28: \n29: ## Dependencies\n30: \n31: - `net/http` 标准库\n32: - 可能的第三方 HTTP 路由库（待设计确认）\n33: - 日志库（pkg/logging 或第三方）\n34: \n35: ## Deliverables\n36: \n37: | File | Description |\n38: |------|-------------|\n39: | `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` | HTTP 服务器核心实现 |\n40: | `pkg/workloadmanager/router.go` | 路由配置与中间件 |\n41: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/` | Handler 接口与基础实现 |\n42: | `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/` | 中间件实现 |\n43: \n44: ## Acceptance Criteria\n45: \n46: - [ ] HTTP 服务器支持优雅启动和关闭\n47: - [ ] 路由框架可扩展，支持标准 RESTful API\n48: - [ ] 中间件链可配置\n49: - [ ] 健康检查端点可访问\n50: - [ ] 错误响应格式统一\n51: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n52: \n53: ## References\n54: \n55: - Go net/http 文档: https://pkg.go.dev/net/http\n\n(End of file - total 55 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，包括:\n- HTTP 服务器配置与生命周期管理\n- 路由设计与中间件架构\n- 请求/响应数据结构定义\n- 健康检查与指标暴露端点\n- 错误处理与日志记录机制","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/spec.md","time":{"start":1775844552048,"end":1775844552060}}}}
